Package oracle.jbo.jbotester Description

Contains the implementation of the Business Component Browser.

Business Component Browser.

The Business Component Browser is a tool that can be used to test BC4J business components.

The Business Component Browser can be launched within JDeveloper. Select 'Run' or 'Debug' from the context menu of an Application Module in an ADF Business Components project to launch the Business Component Browser using the default configuration. Select 'Run' or 'Debug' from a non-default configuration launches the Business Component Browser with the selected configuration.

This package is not intended to be subclassed.
